*libprojectm-0.99-r1 (11 Mar 2007)

  11 Mar 2007; Peter Weller <welp@gentoo.org> +files/libprojectm-fbsd.patch,
  +libprojectm-0.99-r1.ebuild:
  Added patch to let it compile on x86-fbsd, keyworded x86-fbsd

  11 Mar 2007; Bryan Østergaard <kloeri@gentoo.org>
  libprojectm-0.99.ebuild:
  Alpha love.

  08 Mar 2007; Jason Wever <weeve@gentoo.org> libprojectm-0.99.ebuild:
  Added ~sparc keyword wrt bug #168465.

  26 Feb 2007; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> libprojectm-0.99.ebuild:
  Marked ~hppa (bug #168465).

  26 Feb 2007; Tony Vroon <chainsaw@gentoo.org> libprojectm-0.99.ebuild:
  Keyword ~ppc & ~ppc64. Tested with GCC 4.1.2; 64UL.

  13 Nov 2006; Andrej Kacian <ticho@gentoo.org> libprojectm-0.99.ebuild:
  Added ~x86 keyword, bug #154846.

*libprojectm-0.99 (06 Nov 2006)

  06 Nov 2006; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> +metadata.xml,
  +libprojectm-0.99.ebuild:
  Initial import, ProjectM library, thanks to all the users submitting ebuilds
